    "To address the problem of DDoS attacks in smart grids, (Nagaraj et al. 2021) innovatively utilized graph neural networks and graph pooling techniques by combining supervised graph deep learning and unsupervised learning methods to achieve effective detection of DDoS attacks and accurate identification of attacked entities.",
